                    <p rend="flushleft">I <hi rend="italic">Deputies Report and Agenda</hi></p>
                    <p>The Council heard the Deputies’ Report, presented by the Chairman of the
                        day.</p>
                    <p>The Council decided to examine first of all the question of the Peace
                        Conference (draft invitations and rules of procedure), next the question of
                        Italian reparation (final text) and then the question of Germany.</p>
                    <p>The questions appearing in point 3 of document <gloss target="#t_CFM461">CFM
                            (46)</gloss> 191<note n="60" xml:id="d245fn60">The agenda set forth in
                                <gloss target="#t_CFM461">C.F.M.(46)</gloss> 191, July 5, 1946, is
                            contained in footnote 56, <ref target="#pg_781">p. 781</ref>.</note>
                        were referred back to the Deputies, who should report whether or not they
                        had been able to reach an agreement on these various points.</p>
                    <pb facs="0825" n="801" xml:id="pg_801"/>
                    <p rend="flushleft">II <hi rend="italic">Peace Conference</hi> (<hi rend="italic">Draft Invitations and Rules of Procedure</hi>)</p>
                    <p>After an exchange of views on this question, the Council instructed the
                        Deputies to resume study of the matter on the following day, July 6, at
                        10:00 a.m. and report to the Council on its afternoon meeting.</p>
                    <p rend="flushleft">III <hi rend="italic">Reparation Due From Italy</hi></p>
                    <p>The Council instructed the Deputies to draw up, in accordance with the
                        instructions given them at the 34th meeting of the Council, a complete
                        document on reparation from Italy which would include a reference to the
                        claims of Allied nations other than the U.S.S.R. and which would be
                        submitted to the Council at the next meeting.</p>
                    <p rend="flushleft">IV <hi rend="italic">Next Meeting of the Council</hi></p>
                    <p>Saturday, July 6, at 4:00 p.m.</p>
